sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User (Buyer)
    participant UI as User UI (EventDetails)
    participant BE as Backend API
    participant EP as EventPayoutService
    participant ST as Stripe
    participant OUI as Organizer UI (Finance)
    participant AUI as Admin UI (Payout Mgmt)

    U->>UI: Select ticket tiers and checkout
    UI->>BE: POST /payments/{paymentIntentId}/confirm
    UI->>BE: POST /user-tickets (eventId, tierId, qty, paymentIntentId)
    BE-->>UI: Ticket records created
    UI-->>U: Navigate /payment-success + tickets/QR

    Note over BE,EP: Scheduled every 15 minutes\nSync payouts + auto-release job
    BE->>EP: summarize succeeded payments by event/currency
    EP->>EP: Create/Update EventPayout row\nreleaseAt = eventEndAt + 1 day\nstatus = SCHEDULED|READY|HELD|PAID|FAILED

    alt releaseAt reached + Stripe connected + not manual
        EP->>ST: Create Transfer(netPayout)
        ST-->>EP: transfer id or error
        EP->>EP: status -> PAID or FAILED
    else not eligible yet
        EP->>EP: keep SCHEDULED/READY
    end

    OUI->>BE: GET /organizers/stripe/payouts/preview
    BE-->>OUI: Event payout preview rows
    OUI-->>U: Show Event, Net, ReleaseAt, Status
    OUI-->>U: Show status-change banners (dismiss / clear all)

    AUI->>BE: GET /admin/payouts/events/preview?status=
    BE-->>AUI: Event payout preview rows
    AUI-->>AUI: Filter by SCHEDULED|READY|HELD|PAID|FAILED
    AUI->>BE: Hold / Release / PayNow / Retry / RetryFailedBulk
    BE->>EP: Execute admin payout action
    EP-->>AUI: Updated status + payout data

    AUI->>BE: GET /admin/payouts/pending
    AUI->>BE: POST /admin/payouts/manual
    AUI->>BE: PUT /admin/payouts/{id}/sent OR DELETE /admin/payouts/{id}
    BE-->>AUI: Manual payout lifecycle updates
